hadiths[93]{hadithnumber,text}:
0,"shuru sabse zyada raham karne waale, hamesha meherbani karne waley Allah ke naam se. tamam tar hamd w sana sarey jahaanon ke paalne waley Allah ke liye aur behtreen jazaa taqwa ikhtiyar karne walon ke liye hai. Allah khaatimul-anbiya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par apni rehmat nazil farmaai aur tamam nabiyon aur rasulon par bhii. iske baad : Allah aap par raham farmaai ! bila shubah aap ne apne paida karne waley ki taufeeq se ye zikr kya hai ke aap Deen ke tariqon aur ehkaam ke barey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( ummat tak) pahunchne wali tamam hadison ko unki naqal ki hui sanadon samet jaanna chahtey hain aur un hadison ko bhi jo sawab aur azaab, raghbat dilaane aur daraane aur un jaisi dusri chizon ke barey mein hain aur ahale-ilm ne aik doosrey se lin aur pahunchain. Allah aap ki rehnumai farmaai ! aap chahtey hain ke ye tamam hadisein shumar karke majmooey ki shakl mein aap ki pahunch mein lai jaein. aap ne mujh se ye mutalba kya hai ke main un hadison ko zyada takraar ke baghair mukhtasar karke aap ke liye aik kitab ki shakl mein kar dun, kyonke aap samajhtey hain ke ye (baar-baar dohraya jana) un hadison ko achi tarah samajhney aur unse nateeja nikaalne mein aap ke liye rukawat ki wajah banega jo ke aapka (asl) maqsad hai. (Allah aapko izzat de!) aapne jis cheez ka ( mujh se) mutalba kya hai, jab maine iske aur us se hasil hone-waale nateejon ke barey mein ghaur w fikr kya to (mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke) insha-Allah iske nataaij qabile-tareef, aur faayede yaqeeni hongey. aur jab aapne mujh se us kaam ki zahmat uthaney ko kaha to mujhey yaqin ho gaya ke agar mujhey uski taufeeq mili aur Allah ki taraf se iske mukammal honey ka faisla hua to pahlaa shakhs, jisey doosrey logon se qabl us se khas taur par fayda hoga, wo mein khud hoonga. iski wujuhat itni zyada hain ke unka zikr baat ko lamba kar dega, albatta iska khulasa ye hai ke un khususiyaat ki haamil kam hadison ko mehfooz rakhna aur unmein achi tarah maharat hasil karna insan ke liye Kasir hadison ko sanbhaalney ki nisbat zyada aasan hai, khususan Awam mein se aik aisey shakhs ke liye jo us waqt tak unmein (se sahi aur zaeef ke barey mein bhi) imtiyaz nahi kar sakta jab tak koi doosra usey us farq se aagah na kare. jab mamla isi tarah hai jaisey ham ne bayan kya to kam tadaad mein sahi ( hadisein ( chun lena Kasir tadaad mein zaeef hadison ko jama karne se kahin behtar hai. ye baat (apni jagah ( durust hai ke bahut si hadison ko ikattha karne aur mukarrar (baar-baar aai hui) ( hadison ( ko jama karne ke bhi kuchh faayede hain, khususan un logon ke liye jinhein is ( ilm ( mein kisi qadr shuoor aur asbaab w-ilal (cause and effect) ki marifat se nawaza gaya hai. Allah ki marzi se aisa insan un khususiyaat ki wjah se jo usey ata ki gaee hain, Kasir hadison ke majmooey se fayda hasil kar sakta hai lekin jahan tak aam logon ka talluq hai jo shuoor w marifat rakhney waley khawaas se mukhtalif hain, wo kam hadison ki marifat se bhi aajiz hain to unke liye Kasir hadison ke husool mein koi fayda nahi. phir aap ne jis ( kitab (ka mutalba kya ham insha-Allah us iltizaam ke sath uski takhreej ( mukhtalif pahluon se uski wazaahat (aur taaleef ki shuruat kartey hain jiska mein aap ke samney zikr karne laga hun aur wo ye hai ke ham un tamam hadison ko ley lengey jo sanad ke aitibaar se Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan ki gain aur takraar ke baghair unhein teen qismein aur (bayan karne waale) logon ke teen tabqon ke mutabiq taqseem karengey, siwaey-iske ke koi aisa maqam aa jaey jahan kisi hadis ko dobara zikr kiye baghair chaara na ho, ( maslan : ( usmein koi mana zyada ho ya koi sanad aisi ho jo kisi illat ya sabab ki bina par dusri sanad ke pahlu-b-pahlu aai ho kyonke hadis mein aik zayed ma'na, jiski zarurat ho, aik mukammal hadis ke qaaim maqam hota hai, isliye aisi hadis ko , jis mein hamara bayan ki hui koi (manwi) izafa paya jata hai, dobara laey baghair chaara nahi ya jab mumkin hua to ham us mana ko ikhtisar ke sath poori hadis se alag ( karke ( bayan kar dengey lekin kabhi-kabhi usey poori hadis se alag karna mushkil hota hai aur jab uski gunjaaish na ho to usey asl shakl mein dobara bayan karna zyada mehfooz hota hai, albatta jahan hamarey liye usey mukammal taur par dohraney se bachna mumkin hoga aur) kaamil shakl mein) hamein uski zarurat na hogi to ham insha-Allah us se ijtinab karengey. jahan tak pehli qism ka talluq hai (is mein) ham ye koshish karengey ke unhi hadison ko tarjeeh dein jo dusri hadison ki nisbat ( fanni ( Khaamiyon se zyada mehfooz aur zyada paak hon, yani unke riwayat bayan karne waley ( rawi ( naql hadis mein sihat aur bharose rakhney waley hon, unki riwayat mein shadeed ikhtilaf paya jaey na (alfaz w maana ko) bahut burey tareeqey se khalt-malt kya gaya ho jis tarah ke bahut se hadisein bayan karne walon mein paya gaya hai aur unki riwayat mein ye cheez waazeh ho chuki hai. jab ham us qism ke) qaabile-bharosa ( logon ki bayan ki hui riwayaton ka ihaata kar lengey to iskey baad aisi riwayat laaengey jinki sanadon mein koi aisey rawi maujood hongey jo pahle tabqe jaisey ( rawiyon ke) hifz w itqaan (mahaarat) se muttasif nahi lekin wo bhi) unhi mein se hain) chahey un sifaat mein unse zara kam hain jinko unse muqaddam rakha gaya hai lekin iffat , sachchey aur ilm se lagaaw aur dilchaspi rakhney jaisi sifaat unmein aam hon, jis tarah Ata-bin-Saaib , Yazeed bin abi-Ziyad, Lais bin abi Saleem aur unki tarah ke (doosrey ( haameleen aasaar aur khabron ko pahunchane waley hain. ye hazraat halaanki ahale-ilm ke yahan ilm aur iffat ( jaisi sifaat ( mein Maruf hain lekin unke ham Asr logon mein se ( kuchh ( doosrey hazraat aisey hain jo itqaan (mahaarat) aur riwayat ki sihat ke mamley main apne maqam aur martabey ke eitibaar se unse afzal hain. uski wjah ye hai ke ahale-ilm ke yahan ye ( hifz w itqaan (mahaarat) ( aik bahut uncha martaba aur aik aalaa tareen sifat hai. aap dekhtey nahi ke un teenon hazraat : ata , Yazeed aur Leis , jinka ham ne abhi naam liya, ka mawazna (comparison) hadis ke hifz w itqaan (mahaarat) mein Mansoor bin Motamir , Sulaiman Aamash aur Ismail bin abi Khalid se karein to unhein aap un hazraat se khaasey faasley par paeingey , ye unke qareeb bhi nahi aa patey . maahireene-ilme-hadees ko us barey mein koi shak nahi ke Mansoor , Aamash aur Ismail ke yahan hifz ki sihat aur hadis bayan karne mein maharat ki jo sifaat ahle-ilm ko nazar aati hain unke nazdeek wo ata , Yazeed aur Leis ke yahan is tarah Maruf nahi. agar aap (doosrey ( barabar ke logon ke darmyan mawazna (comparison) karein to ( bhi) yahi maajraa ( samney aata ( hai, maslan : aap Ibne-Aun aur Ayub sakhtiyan ka ( mawazna (comparison) ( Auf-bin-abi Jameela aur Ashas Humraani se karein. ye donon ( bhi usi tarah) Hasan Basri aur Ibne-Sirin ke shagird hain jis tarah Ibne-Aun aur Ayub unke shagird hain lekin un donon aur un donon ke darmyan kamaal Fazal aur sihat naql ke eitibaar se bahut bada fasla paya jata hai. Auf aur Ashas bhi agarche ahale-ilm ke yahan sachchey w amanat se hatey huey nahi ( maane jaate ( lekin jahan tak martabey ka talluq hai to ahale-ilm ke yahan haqiqat wahi hai jo ham ne bayan ki. ham ne naam zikr karke misal isliye di hai taake us shakhs ke liye, jo ahale-ilm ke yahan haameleen hadis ki darja bandi ke tareeqey se na-waqif hai, ye misal aisa waazeh nishan Sabit ho jiske zariey se wo mukammal jankari hasil kar ley aur uncha darja rakhney waley ko iske martabey se ghataaey aur na kam darjey waley ko iske martabey se badhaatey , har aik ko iska haq de aur uske martabey par rakhey . Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat bayan ki gaee, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha ke ham logon ko unke martabon par rakhein. iske sath hi Allah ka hukm hai jo Quran ne bayan farmaya : har ilm waley se uper aik ilm rakhney wala hai. ham hadison rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko apni zikr karda Suraton ke mutabiq taaleef karengey. jo hadison un logon se marwi (bayan) hain jo ( tamam ( maahireene-ilme-hadees ya unmein se aksar ke nazdeek muttahim hain, ham unki riwayat se koi sarokaar na rakhengey, jaisey : Abdullah-bin Miswar abu-Jafar madaaini, Amr bin Khalid, Abdul-Quddoos shaami, Muhammad-bin-Saeed masloob, Ghiyas bin Ibrahim (Alaihissalam), Sulaiman bin-Amr Nakhai aur un jaisey doosrey logon ki bayan ki hui riwayaton se bhi, jin par hadeesein ghadney aur riwayat saazi ke ilzaamaat hain. isi tarah wo log jinki bayan ki hui riwayaton ki ghalib tadaad munkar aur ghalat ( hadison ( par mushtamil hai, ham unki hadison se bhi bachengey. kisi hadis bayan karne waley ki munkar riwayat ki nishani ye hai ke jab uski riwayat ki hui hadis ka doosrey ashaab hifz aur maqbool ( muhaddeseen ( ki riwayat se mawazna (comparison) kya jaey to wo unki riwayat ke mukhalif ho ya unke sath muwafiq na ho paaey. jab kisi ki aksar bayan ki hui riwayaten is tarah ki hon to wo matrookul-hadees hota hai, uski riwayat ghair maqbool hoti hain, (ijtihaad w istinbaat (nateeja nikaalne) ke liye) istemal nahi hotiin. us qism ke hadis ke raviyon mein Abdullah-bin muharrir, Yahya-bin-abi-Unaisa, Jarrah-bin-Minhal abu-Atwaf, Ibaad-bin-Kaseer , Husain bin-Abdullah-bin Zameera , Umar-bin-Sehban aur is tarah ke doosrey munkar riwayat bayan karne waley log shamil hain, ham unki riwayat ka rukh nahi kartey na un riwayat se koi sarokaar hi rakhtey hain. kyonke hadis mein munfarid rawi ki riwayat qabool karne ke mutaalliq ahale-ilm ka Maruf mazhab aur unka faisla ye hai ke agar wo ( rawi ( aam taur par ahale-ilm w hifz siqaat (tehzeeb) ki muwafiqat karta hai aur us ne gehrai mein ja kar unki muwafiqat ki hai to aisi sura mein agar wo ( munfarid ( koi aisa izafa bayan karta hai jo iske doosrey ham maktabon ke yahan nahi hai to uska ye izafa ( muhaddeseen ke yahan ( qabool kya jaeyga lekin jis (hadees bayan karne waale) ko aap dekhein ke wo imam Zohri jaisey Jaleelul-qadr ( muhaddis ( se riwayat bayan karta hai jinke Kasir tadaad mein aisey shagird hain jo (hadeeson ke) Hafiz hain, unki aur doosrey (muhaddeseen) ki riwayat ke maahir hain ya wo Hisham-bin-Urwa jaisey (Imam taabein) se riwayat karta hai. un donon ki hadisein to ahale-ilm ke yahan khub phaili hui hain, wo sab unki riwayat mein (eik doosrey ke saath) saajhedari rakhtey hain aur un donon ki aksar hadison mein unke shagird aik doosrey se muttafiq hain. aur ye shakhs un donon ya unmein se kisi aik se bahut si aisi hadison riwayat karey jin mein unke shagirdon mein se iske sath koi aur Sharik nahi to us jaisey logon se us qism ki koi hadis qabool karna jaaiz nahi. Allah ( hi ( zyada jaanney wala hai. ham ne hadis aur ashaab hadis ( muhaddeseen (ke tareeq kaar ka kuchh hissey har us shakhs ki tawajjoh ke liye jo unke rastey par chalnaa chahta hai aur jisey uski taufeeq naseeb hoti hai, tafseel se bayan kar diya hai. insha-Allah ham (is tareeqe-kaar ki) mazeed sharah (explaination) aur wazahat kitab ke un maqamat par karengey jahan malool hadison (jin mein koi khufiya illat paai jati hai) ka zikr hoga, (yani ( jab ham wahan pahunchein gey jahan us ( mozu ( ki sharah (explaination) aur wazaahat ka munasib mauqa hoga. insha-Allah taala . us ( wazaahat (ke ba'd, Allah aap par raham farmaai ! ( ham ye kehna chahtey hain ke) agar ham ne apne aapko muhaddis ke mansab par faaiz karne waley bahut se logon ki zaeef hadison aur munkar riwayat ke bayan ko tark karne jaisey maamlaat mein, jinka iltizaam unke liye lazim tha, ghalat karrwaiyan na dekhi hotin, aur agar unhon-ne sahi riwayat ke bayan par iktifako tark na kya hota, jinhein un qaabile-bharosa rawiyon ne bayan kya jo sachchey w amanat mein Maruf hain, wo bhi unke us aetraaf ke baad ke jo kuchh wo ( seedhey saadhey ( kam aql logon ke samney be parwaaii se bayan kiye ja rahe hain, iska aksar hissey ghair maqbool hai, un logon se naql kya gaya hai jin se riwayat leney par ahale-ilm razi nahi aur jin se riwayat karne ko) badey badey ( aimma hadis, maslan Maalik-bin-Anas, Shoba bin Hujjaaj, Sufiyan-bin-Uena, Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan, Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi waghaira qaabil mazammat samajhtey hain. agar ham ne ye sab na dekha hota to aap ne ( sahi w zaeef mein) imtiyaz aur) sirf sahi ke) husool ke hawale se jo mutalba kya hai usey qabool karna aasan na hota. lekin jis tarah ham ne aapko qaum ki taraf se kamzor aur majhool sanadon se ( bayan ki gai) munkar hadison ko bayan karne aur unhein aisey Awam mein, jo un( hadison (ke uyoob se na-waqif hain, phailaaney ke barey mein bataya to ( sirf ( usi bina par hamarey dil ke liye aap ke mutaalbey ko taslim karna aasan hua. Allah aapko taufeeq se nawaazey ! aap jaan lein ke har aisey insan par jo sahi aur zaeef riwayat aur qaabile-bharosa aur muttahim rawiyon ke beech imtiyaz kar sakta hai, ye farz Aaiz hota hai ke wo un hadison ke siwa , jinke sahi turq (Hadeeson ke jama karne ka silsilewaar tareeqa) se hasil honey ka aur jinke naql karne walon ke ghair muttahim honey ka ilm hai, koi aur riwayat bayan na karey aur un riwayat (ke bayan ( se bachchey jo muttahim logon aur bidat ka irtikaab karne waley dushmanon se marwi (bayan) hon. is barey mein ham ne jo kaha, iske bar-aks ko tark kartey huey usi ko ikhtiyar karna lazim hai, Allah tabarak w taala ka ye farman hai :  یٰۤاَیُّہَا الَّذِیۡنَ اٰمَنُوۡۤا اِنۡ جَآءَکُمۡ فَاسِقٌۢ بِنَبَاٍ فَتَبَیَّنُوۡۤا اَنۡ تُصِیۡبُوۡا قَوۡمًۢا بِجَہَالَۃٍ فَتُصۡبِحُوۡا عَلٰی مَا فَعَلۡتُمۡ نٰدِمِیۡنَ, 'aey eman waalo! agar koi fasiq (gunahgaar) tumharey paas koi khabar lekar aaey to tahqeeq kar liya karo) mubaada (ke kisi qaum par naadaanii se ja pado , phir apne kiye par pachhtaaney lago. , aur Allah jal shana ne farmaya : ( مِمَّنۡ تَرۡضَوۡنَ مِنَ الشُّہَدَآءِ ( un gawaahon mein se jo tumhen pasand hun. (usi tarah) izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne (ye bhi) farmaya : ( وَّ اَشۡہِدُوۡا ذَوَیۡ عَدۡلٍ مِّنۡکُمۡ ( apne mein se do moa'tabar logon ko gawah bana lo. un tamam aayatein se Sabit hua ke fasiq ki) pahunchai hui ( khabar saaqit ( bharose ke aitibaar se) aur naqabile-qabool hai aur jo shaahid adl nahi uski gawahi mardood hai. khabar agarche kuchh wajhon se shahadat ( gawahi ( se mukhtalif mana ki haamil hai lekin donon apne badey aur buniyadi mafhoom mein aapasii Sharik hain. jahan ahale-ilm ke yahan fasiq ki khabar naqabile-qabool hai wahan un tamam ke yahan uski gawahi ( bhi) mardood hai. ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) sunnat naqabile-qabool khabar ki riwayat ke inkar ko) jyon ka tyon ( isi tarah waazeh karti hai jis tarah Quran fasiq ki khabar ke inkar par dalaalat karta hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marwi mashhoor hadis hai : jisne mujh se ( aisi ( hadis bayan ki jisey wo janta hai ke jhoot hai to wo (2) jhooton mein se aik ( jhoota ( hai."
1,"Allaah aapako taufeeq de, jaan leejiye ki jo shakhs sahee aur zaeef hadis mein farq aur tameez karane ki salaahiyat rakhta ho aur vo bharosemand raviyon (hadees bayan karnevalon) aur muttahim raaviyon (jinapar jhoot vagaira ka ilzam laga ho) ko pehchanata bhee ho to us par vaajib hai ki sivaaey us hadis ke kisi aur hadis ko bayan na kare jo sanad ke aitibaar se sahi ho aur usake bayan karanevaale wo log hon jinke aib aur buraii logon ke saamne na aai hun. aur un logon ki hadis bayan karane se bachen jinapar kisi tarah ka ilzam lagaya gaya ho ya jo log dushmani rakhte hon ya jo log Deen mein nai baat (bidat) paida karte hon. jo kuchh hamne bayan kiya uski daleel ye hai ki Allah rabbul-izzat ne faramaaya ""aey eimaan-walo! agar tumhaare paas koi fasiq (jhoota ya bad-amal) khabar lekar aaey to tahqeeq (jaanch-padtaal) kar liya karo, aisa na ho ki tum kisi giroh ko an-jaane mein nuqsan pahuncha baitho aur phir apne kiye par sharminda ho."" (49:06) doosri jagah faramaaya ""gawaah bana lo do mardon ko, agar 2 mard na hon to ek mard aur 2 aurtein hi sahi, ye gavaah tumhaare pasandida logon mein se hun. (gavaahee ke liye, yaanee jo sachche aur nek malum hon)"" (2:282) ek aur jagah Farmaya ""aur apne mein se do aadil (insaaf-pasand) logon ko gawah bana lo."" (65:02) to in tamam aayaton se malum hua ki fasiq aur jhoote ki baat ka koi bharosa nahin hai. wo naqabile-qabool hai. aur gair-aadil shakhs ki khabar qaabile-radd hai. aur isi tarah hadis sharif se ye bhi baat malum hoti hai ke munkar riwayat ka bayan karna ( jiske ghalat honey ka imkan ho) durust nahi jaisey Quran se malum hota hai aur wo hadis wahi hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se shohrat k sath manqul hai ke farmaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne : ''jo shakhs mujh se hadis naql karey aur wo khayal karta ho ke ye jhoot hai to wo khud jhoota hai.'' imaam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne apni asnaad se riwayat kya saiyedna Samra-bin-Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) aur saiyedna Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (yani wahi hadis jo uper guzri ke jo shakhs mujh se hadis naql karey aur wo samajhta ho ke ye jhoot hai to wo khud jhoota hai)."
2,"Abu-Bakar bin abi Sheba, Muhammad-bin-Musanna aur ibne-Bashar ne kaha : ham se Muhammad-bin-Jafar (ghandar ( ne Shoba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne Rabai-bin-Hirash se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, jab wo khutba de rahe they, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ""mujh par jhoot na bolo, bila shubah jisne mujh par jhoot bola wo jahannam mein dakhil hoga."
3,"Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : mujhey tumharey samney zyada hadisein bayan karne se ye baat rokti hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha : jisne jan-boojhkar mujh par jhoot bola wo aag mein apna thikana bana ley."
4,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne jan-boojhkar mujh par jhoot bola wo aag mein apna thikana bana ley."
5,"Saeed-bin-Ubaid ne kaha : hamein Ali-bin Rabee waalbi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : main masjid mein aaya aur (us waqt) Hazrat Mughira (bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu)) Kufa ke ameer ( governer ( they : Mughira ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : mujh par jhoot bolnaa is tarah nahi jaisey ( mere ilawa ( kisi aik ( aam aadmi ( par jhoot bolnaa hai, jisne jaan-bojh kar mujh par jhoot bola wo jahannam mein apna thikana bana ley.'"
6,"Muhammad-bin Qais Asadi ne Ali-bin Rabee Asadi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki lekin 'bila shubah mujh par jhoot bolnaa is tarah nahi jaisey kisi aik ( aam ( aadmi par jhoot bolnaa hai. (ka jumla ( bayan nahi kya."
7,"Ubaidullah-bin-Muaz bin Anbari aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi donon ne kaha : ham se Shoba ne bayan kya, unhon-ne Khubaib bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hafs bin Aasim se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aadmi ke jhoota honey ke liye yahi kafi hai ke wo har suni hui baat bayan kar de.'"
8,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba ne Ali-bin Hafs se, unhon-ne Shoba se, unhon-ne Khubaib bin Abdur-Rehman se, unhon-ne Hafs bin Aasim se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske jaisi riwayat bayan ki."
9,"Yahya bin Yahyaa, Hasheem, Sulaiman taimii, abu-Usmaan nehdi se riwayat hai, kaha : Umar-bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aadmi ke liye jhoot se itna kafi hai (jis ki bina par wo jhoota qarar diya ja sakta hai) ke wo har suni hui baat bayan kar de."
10,"ibne- Wahab ne khabar di, kaha : Malik (bin Anas ( ne mujh se kaha : mujhey malum hai ke aisa aadmi ( sahi ( Salim nahi hota jo har suni hui baat ( aagey ( bayan kar de, wo kabhi imam nahi bin sakta ( jabke ( wo har suni hui baat ( aagey ( bayan kar deta hai."
11,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna , Abdur-Rehman , Sufiyan , Abu-Ishaq , abul-Ahwas ne Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : aadmi ke jhoot mein yahi kafi hai ke wo har suni hui baat bayan kar de."
12,Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne kaha : maine Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi se suna keh rahe they : aadmi us waqt tak imam nahi bin sakta ke log uski iqtida (pairvi) karein yahan tak ke wo suni-sunai kuchh baton (ko bayan karne) se baaz aa jaaey.
13,"Sufiyan bin Husain se riwayat hai ke Ayas bin Muawiya ne mujh se mutalba kya aur kaha, main tumhen dekhta hun tum Quran ke ilm se shadeed raghbat rakhtey ho tum mere samney aik sura padho aur uski tafseer karo taake jo tumhen ilm hai main bhi usey dekhun. kaha, maine aisa kya to unhon-ne mujh se farmaya jo baat main tum se kehney laga hun usey meri taraf se hamesha yad rakhna, na-pasandida (munkar) riwayat (ko bayan karne) se bachna ! kyonke aisa na honey ke barabar hai ke kisi ne ye kaam kya ho (munkar riwayat bayan kin) aur wo apni zaat mein zaleel ( na ( hua ho aur uski bayan ki hui hadis ko jhoota ( na ( samjha gaya ho."
14,"abu-Taahir, Hurmala bin Yahya , ibne- Wahab , Yunus , ibne-Shahab, Ubaidullah-bin-Abdullaah-bin-Utba, Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : tum kisi qaum ke samney aisi hadis bayan nahi kartey jis (ke sahi mafhoom ( tak unki aqlein nahi pahunch saktin magar wo unmein se kuchh ke liye fitney (ka sabab) bin jati hain."
15,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer , Zuhair-bin-Harab , Abdullah-bin Yazeed , Sad bin abi-Ayub , abu-Haani ne abu-Usmaan Muslim-bin Yasar se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : meri ummat ke aakhiri zamaney mein aisey log hongey jo tumharey samney aisi hadisein bayan karengey jo na tumne suni hongi na tumharey bap-dada ne, tum is tarah ke logon se door rehna.'"
16,"Hurmala bin Yahya , Abdullah-bin Hurmala bin Imran tajeebii , ibne- Wahab , Sharaheel bin Yazeed kehtey hain : mujhey Muslim-bin Yasar ne bataya ke unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aakhiri zamaney main ( aisey ( dajjal ( faraib kaar ( kazzaab (bahut bade jhootey) hongey jo tumharey paas aisi hadisein laaengey jo na tum ne suni hongi aur na tumharey baap-dada ne. tum unse door rehna (kahin) wo tumhen gumrah na kar dein aur tumhen fitney mein na daal dein.'"
17,"abu-Saeed ashajj , Wakee, Aamash , Musaiyab bin Raafe, Aamir bin Abda se riwayat hai, kaha : Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : bila shubah shaitan kisi aadmi ki shakl ikhtiyar karta hai, phir logon ke paas aata hai aur unhein jhoot ( par mabni ( koi hadis sunata hai, phir wo bikhar jatey hain, unmein se koi aadmi kehta hai : maine aik aadmi se ( hadis) suni hai, main uska chehra to pehchanta hun par uska naam nahi janta, wo hadis suna raha tha."
18,"Muhammad-bin Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq , Mamar , ibne- Taaus , Taaus ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin Amr-bin-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : samandar (ki teh ( mein bahut se shaitan qaid hain jinhein Hazrat Sulaiman ‌(al) ne baandha tha, waqt aa raha hai ke wo niklengey aur logon ke samney Quran padhengey."
19,"Muhammad-bin Ibad , Saeed-bin-Umar , ash-Asaa, ibne-Uena, Saeed, Sufiyan , Hisham bin Juhair ne Taaus se riwayat ki, kaha : ye (unki murad Basheer-bin-kab se thi) Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur unhein hadisein sunaney laga, Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : falan-falan hadis dohrao. us ne dohra dein, phir unke samney hadisein bayan kin. unhon-ne isse kaha : falan hadis dobara sunao. us ne unke samney dohraain, phir aap se kaha : main nahi janta ke aap ne meri ( bayan ki hui ( saari hadison pehchan li hain aur us hadis ko munkar jana hai ya sab ko munkar jana hai aur usey pehchan liya hai? Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne us se kaha : jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jhoot nahi bola jata tha ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadisein bayan kartey they, phir jab log (har ( mushkil aur aasan sawari par Sawar honey lagey ( bila tameez sahi w zaeef riwayat bayan karne lagey ( to ham ne ( seedhey-seedhey (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan karna tark kar diya."
20,"Muhammad-bin Raafe , Abdur-Razzaq , ibne- Taaus , Taaus ke betey ne apne walid ( Taaus ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadisein hifz kartey they aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( marwi) hadis ki hifazat ki jati thi magar jab se tum logon ne ( baghair tameez ke) har mushkil aur aasan par sawari shuru kar di to phir mamla hath se jata raha (yani phir hamne riwayat bayan karni band kari dii)."
21,"Mujahid se riwayat hai ke Bashir-bin-kab Adwi Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaya aur us ne hadisein bayan kartey huey kehna shuru kar diya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu)) ne ye rawaiya rakha ke) na usko dhyaan se suntey they na uski taraf dekhtey they. wo kehney laga : aey Ibne-Abbas ! mere sath kya ( mamla ( hai, mujhey nazar nahi aata ke aap meri ( bayan ki hui ( hadis sun rahe hain? mein aapko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis suna raha hun aur aap suntey hi nahi. Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : aik waqt aisa tha ke jab ham kisi ko ye kehtey suntey : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya to hamari nazrein fauran uski taraf uth jaatiin aur ham kaan laga kar ghaur se uski baat suntey, phir jab logon ne ( bila tameez (har mushkil aur aasan par sawari ( shuru ( kar di to ham ne logon se koi hadis qabool na ki siwaey us ( hadis) ke jisey ham jantey they."
22,"ibne-abi-Mulaika se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf likha aur unse darkhaast ki ke wo mere liye aik kitab likhein aur (jin baton ki sihat mein koi shak ho ya jo na likhney ki hon wo) baatein mujh se chipa lein. unhon-ne farmaya : ladka khalis hadison ka talabgaar hai, main uske liye ( hadis se mutaalliq ( tamam maamlo mein) sahi ka ( intikhab karunga aur) mozu aur ghadi hui hadison ko) hata doonga (kaha : unhon-ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke faisley mangwaaey (aur unmein se cheezein likhnii shuru kiin aur (ye hua ke) koi cheez guzarti to farmatey : b-khudaa ! ye faisla Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne nahi kya, siwaey iske ke) khuda-n-khasta ( wo gumrah ho gaey hon (jab ke aisa nahi hua. ("
23,"Amr-Naqid, Sufiyan-bin-Uena, hishaam-bin-hujair, Taaus se riwayat hai, kaha : Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aik kitab laai gaee jis mein Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke faisley ( likhe huey) they, to unhon-ne is qadr chhod kar baqi (sab kuchh ( mitaa diya aur Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne hath ( jitni lambai (ka ishara kya."
24,"Hasan-bin-Ali Hulwani , yahyaa-bin-aadam , ibne-Idrees , Aamash , Abu-Ishaq se riwayat hai, kaha : jab ( bazahir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam leney waale) logon ne Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad (unke naam par) ye cheezein eiijaad kar lein to unke sathiyon mein se aik shakhs ne kaha : Allah un ( logon ( ko ghaarat karey! unhon-ne kaisa ( azimushshan ( ilm bigaad diya."
25,"Ali-bin-khashram , Abu-Bakar bin Ayash ne hamein bataya , kaha : maine Mughira se suna, farmatey they : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hadison mein kisi cheez ki tasdeeq na ki jati thi, siwaey iske jo Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ke shagirdon se riwayat ki gaee ho."
26,"Hasan-bin-Rabee, Hammad-bin-Zaid, Ayyoob, Hisham, Muhammad, Mina Fuzail, Hishaam, Makhlad-bin-Husain, Hishaam, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Sirin se riwayat ki, ye ilme-deen hai, isliye (achi tarah) dekh lo ke tum kin logon se apna Deen akhaz kartey ho."
27,"Aasim ahwal ne Ibne-Sirin se riwayat ki, kaha : ( shuruati daur mein hadis ke aalim ( asnaad ke barey mein koi sawal na kartey they, jab fitna pad gaya to unhon-ne kaha : hamarey samney apne logon (hadees bayan karnewalon) ke naam lo taake ahale-sunnat ko dekh kar unse hadis li jaey aur ahale-bidat ko dekh kar unki hadis qabool na ki jaaey."
28,"Auzai ne Sulaiman-bin-Musa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha, mein Taaus ‌ (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se mila aur unse kaha, mujhey falan shakhs ne is-is tarah hadis sunai. unhon kaha, agar tumharey sahib ( ustad ( poori tarah qaabile-bharosa hain to unse le-lo."
29,"Saeed-bin-Abdul-Azeez ne Sulaiman-bin-Musa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Taaus ‌ (Rahmatullahi-alaih) se kaha : falan ne in-in alfaz se mujhey hadis sunai. unhon-ne kaha : agar tumharey sahib bharose mein poore hain to unse le-lo."
30,"( Abdur-Rehman ( bin-abii-Zanad ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : main Madina mein sau (ahle-ilm) se mila jo ( Deen main to ( mehfooz w maamoon they ( lekin) unse hadis nahi li jati thin, kaha jata tha ye us (ilm (ke ahal nahin."
31,"Misar se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Sad bin Ibrahim (bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ( se suna, keh rahe they : qaabile-bharosa rawiyon ke ilawa aur koi shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hadis bayan na kare."
32,"Muhammad-bin-Abdullah-bin-Qahzaad ne (jo marw ke baashindon mein se hain) kaha : maine Abdan-bin-Usman se suna, keh rahe they : maine Abdullah-bin-Mubarak (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : asnaad (silsila sanad se hadis riwayat karna) Deen mein se hai. agar sanadon ka silsile na hota to jo koi jo kuchh chahta, keh deta (Imam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne) kaha : aur Muhammad-bin-Abdullah ne kaha : mujhey abbaas-bin-abi-razma ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Abdullah (bin-Mubarak) ko ye kehtey huey suna : hamarey aur logon ke darmyan (faisla-kun cheez, bayan ki janey wali khabron ke) paaun, yani sanadein hain (jin par riwayat is tarah khadi hoti hain jis tarah jaandaar apne paon par khadey hotey hain) Muhammad (bin-Abdullah-bin-Qahzad) ne kaha maine Abu-Ishaq Ibrahim-bin-Esa Taliqani se suna, kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Mubarak se kaha : abu-abdur-Rehmaan! (wo ( hadis kaisi hai jo (in alfaz mein) aai hai : neki ke baad (doosrii) neki ye hai ke tum apni Namaz ke sath apne waalidain ke liye Namaz padho aur apne rozon ke sath apne waalidain ke liye rozey rakho? kaha, Abdullah (bin-Mubarak) ne kaha : ye kis (ki sanad) se hai, kaha : maine kaha : ye Shahab-bin-Kharash ki (bayaan ki hui) hadis hai, unhon-ne kaha : qabile-bharosa hai, (phir) kis se? kaha : maine kaha : Hujjaj-bin-Dinar se kaha : qabile-bharosa hai (phir) kis se? kaha : maine kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kehney lagey : abu-Ishaq! Hujjaj-bin-Dinar aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan bahut dooriyaan hain jinko paar kartey huey oontniyon ki gardanein kat (kar gir) jati hain lekin sadqa (maiyat ke liye faayde-mand hai is) ke barey mein koi ikhtilaf nahin. muhammad ne kaha : maine Ali-bin-Shaqiq se suna keh rahe they : maine Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ko sab ke samney ye kehtey suna : Amr-bin-Sabit ki (riwayat ki hui) hadis tark kar do, kyonke wo salaf saaleheen ko gaaliyan diya karta thaa."
33,"abu-Nazar Hashim bin-Qasim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham se Buhaiya ke Maula abu-Aqeel (Yahya-bin-Mutawakkil) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : main Qasim-bin-Ubaidullah (bin-Abdullaah-bin-umar jinki walida umme-Abdullah-bint-Qasim-bin-Muhammad-bin-abi-Bakr thin) aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ke paas betha hua tha ke Yahya ne Qasim-bin-Ubaidullah se kaha : janab abu-Muhammad ! aap jaisi shakhsiyat ke liye ye aib hai, bahut badi baat hai ke aap se is Deen ke kisi mamley ke barey mein) kuchh ( puchha jaey aur aap ke paas iske hawale se na ilm ho na koi hal ya (ye alfaz kahey ( na ilm ho na nikalney ki koi raah. to Qasim ne unse kaha : kis wjah se? (Yahya ne) kaha : kyonke aap hidayat ke 2 imamon Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke farzand hain. kaha : Qasim usse kehney lagey : jis shakhs ko Allah ki taraf se aql mili ho, uske nazdeek us se bhi bd-tar baat ye hai ke main ilm ke baghair kuchh keh dun ya usse riwayat karun jo qaabile-bharosa na ho. (ye sun kar yahyaa) khamosh ho gaey aur unhein koi jawab nahi diya."
34,"Bishr-bin-hakam abdii ne mujh se bayan kya, kaha : maine Sufiyan-bin-Uena se suna, keh rahe they : mujh se bahut se logon ne Buhaiya ke Maula abu-Aqeel se (sun kar) riwayat ki ke (kuchh) logon ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik betey se koi baat poochhi jiske barey mein unke ilm mein kuchh na tha to Yahya-bin-Saeed ne unse kaha : main usko bahut badi baat samajhta hun ke aap jaisey insan se (jabke aap hidayat ke 2 imaamon yani umr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke betey hain, koi baat poochhi jaey (aur) iske barey mein aapko kuchh ilm na ho. unhon-ne kaha : ba-khuda ! Allah ke nazdeek aur us shakhs ke nazdeek jisey Allah ne aql di us se bhi badi baat ye hai ke main ilm ke baghair kuchh kahun ya kisi aisey shakhs se riwayat karun jo qaabile-bharosa nahi. (sufiyaan ne) kaha : abu-Aqeel Yahya-bin-Mutawakkil (bhi) unke paas maujood they jab unhon-ne ye baat ki."
35,"Yahya-bin-Saeed ne kaha : maine Sufiyan Sory , Shoba , Malik aur ibne-Uena se aisey aadmi ke barey mein puchha jo hadis mein pori tarah qaabile-bharosa na ho, phir koi aadmi aaey aur mujh se iske barey mein sawal karey? to un sab ne kaha : iske barey mein bata do ke wo poori tarah qaabile-bharosa nahi hai."
36,"Nazar kehtey hain ke Ibne-Aun se Shahar (bin Hoshab ( ki hadis ke barey mein sawal kya gaya, (us waqt) wo (apnii) dahleez par khadey they, wo kehney lagey : unhon (muhaddeseen) ne yaqinan «Shahar» ko matoon (malamati) thehraya hai, Imam Muslim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : logon ki zabanon ne unhein nishana banaya, unke barey mein baatein kin."
37,"hamein Shababa ne bataya , kaha : Shoba ne kaha : main ( Shahar ( se mila lekin (riwaayat hadis ke hawale se) maine unhein ahmiyat nahi di."
38,"Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne kaha : maine Sufiyan Sory se arz kya : bila shubah Ibaad-bin-Kaseer aisa hai jiska haal aapko malum hai. jab wo hadis bayan karta hai to badi baat karta hai, kya aap ki raey hai ke main logon se keh diya karun is se ( hadis) na lo ? Sufiyan kehney lagey : kyon nahi ! Abdullah ne kaha : phir ye ( mera mamool (routine) (ho gaya ke jab main kisi ( ilmi ( majlis mein hota jahan Ibad ka zikr hota to main Deen ke hawale se uski tareef karta aur) sath ye bhi) kehta is se ( hadis) na lo. ham se Muhammad ne bayan kya, kaha : ham se Abdullah-bin-Usman ne bayan kya, kaha : mere walid ne kaha : Abdullah-bin-Mubarak ne kaha : main Shoba tak pahuncha to unhon-ne ( bhi) kaha : ye Ibaad-bin-Kaseer hai tum log us se ( hadis bayan karne mein) ehtiyat karo"
39,"Fazal-bin-Sahal ne bataya , kaha : maine Mu-alla Razi se Muhammad-bin-Saeed ke barey mein, jis se Ibaad-bin-Kaseer ne riwayat ki, puchha to unhon-ne mujhey Esa-bin-Yonus ke hawale se bayan kya, kaha : main iske darwazey par tha, Sufiyan uske paas maujood they jab wo bahar nikal gaya to maine un ( Sufiyan ( se iske barey mein puchha to unhon-ne mujhey bataya ke wo bahut bada jhoota hai."
40,"Muhammad-bin-abi-Itab ne kaha : mujh se Affaan ne Muhammad-bin Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : ham ne nek logon ( soofiya ( ko hadis se badh kar kisi aur cheez mein jhoot bolney wala nahi paya. ibne-abi Attab ne kaha : main Muhammad-bin Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan se mila to us ( baat ke) barey mein poochha, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat kartey huey kaha : tum ahle-khair (parhezgaron) ko hadis se zyada kisi aur cheez mein jhoota nahi paogey Imam Muslim ne kaha ke Yahya-bin-Saeed ne farmaya : unki zaban par jhoot jari ho jata hai, wo jaan-bojh kar jhoot nahi boltey."
41,"Khalifa-bin-Musa ne khabar di, kaha : main Ghalib-bin-Ubaidullah ke yahan aaya to usne mujhey likhwana shuru kya : Mak-hool ne mujh se hadis bayan ki, Mak-hool ne mujh se hadis bayan ki. usi beech mein peshab ne usey majbur kya to wo uth gaya, maine (jo ( uski copy dekhi to is mein is tarah tha : mujhey Aban ne Anas se ye hadis sunai, Aban ne falan se hadis riwayat ki. is par maine usey chhod diya aur uth khada hua. (Imam Muslim ne kaha : (aur maine Hasan-bin-Ali Hulwani se suna, keh rahe they : maine Affaan ki kitab mein abu-miqdaam Hisham ki (wo) riwayat dekhi (jo Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ki hadis hai) (us mein tha :) Hisham ne kaha : mujh se aik shakhs ne jisey Yahya-bin-fulan kaha jata tha, Muhammad-bin-Kab se hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Affaan se kaha : ( ahale-ilm ( kehtey hain : Hisham ne ye ( hadis) Muhammad-bin-Kab se suni thi. to wo kehney lagey : wo ( Hisham ( usi hadis ki wjah se fitney mein padey . (pahley ( wo kaha kartey they : mujhey Yahya ne Muhammad (bin Kab) se riwayat ki, uske baad ye dawa kar diya ke unhon-ne ye (hadees barahe-rast) Muhammad se suni hai."
42,"mujhey Muhammad-bin-Abdullah Qohzaz ne hadis sunai, kaha : maine Abdullah-bin-Usman bin Jabla se suna, keh rahe they : maine Abdullah-bin-Mubarak se kaha : ye kon hai jis se aap ne Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis : Eidul-fitr ka din inaamaat ka din hai. riwayat ki? kaha : Sulaiman-bin Hajjaj, unmein se jo (hadisein) tum ne apne paas (likh ( rakhi hain (ya maine tumhen uski jo hadisein di hain) unmein (achchhi tarah) nazar karna (ghaur kar lena) ibne-Quhzaz ne kaha : maine Wahab-bin-Zama se suna, wo Sufiyaan-bin-Abdul-Malik se riwayat kar rahe they, kaha : Abdullah, yani ibne-Mubarak ne kaha : maine aik dirham ke barabar khoon wali hadis ke rawi Rooh-bin-Ghutaif ko dekha hai. main uske sath aik majlis mein betha to main apne sathiyon se sharm mehsus kar raha tha ke wo mujhey us se hadis bayan karne ke na-pasandida honey ke bawajud iske sath betha dekhein ( uski hadis na-pasandidgi ki wjah se aur uski riwayat mein na maqbooli ki wjah se)"
43,"ibne-Qohzaz ne kaha, maine Wahab se suna, unhon-ne Sufiyan se aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Mubarak se riwayat ki, kaha : Baqiiya zaban ke sachey hain lekin wo har aaney janey waley ( ilme-hadees mein maharat rakhney waley aur na rakhney waley har shakhs) se hadis ley letey hain."
44,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed, Jarir ne Mughira se, unhon-ne Shabi se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey Haris Aawar Hamdani ne hadis sunai aur wo kazzaab tha."
45,"abu-Aamir Abdullah-bin Baraad-Ashari, abu-Usama , Mufazzal-bin-Mughira se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Shabi ko kehtey huey suna : mujh se Haris Aawar ne riwayat bayan ki aur (ye ke) wo gawahi detey hain ke wo ( Haris ( jhooton mein se aik tha."
46,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed, jareer, Mughira ne Ibrahim se riwayat ki, kaha : Alqama ne kaha : maine 2 saal mein Quran padha (ghaur-fikr kartey huey khatm kya.) to Haris ne kaha : Quran aasan hai, wahi us se zyada mushkil hai."
47,"Hajjaaj-bin Shaair , Ahmed bin Yunus ne Ibrahim Nakhai se riwayat ki ke Haris ( Aawar ( ne kaha : maine Quran teen saal mein seekha aur wahi 2 saal main (ya kaha ( : wahi teen saal main aur Quran 2 saal mein."
48,Mansoor aur Mughira ne Ibrahim se riwayat ki ke Haris muttahim rawi hai
49,"Hamza Zayyat se riwayat hai, kaha : Murra Hamdani ne Haris se koi baat suni to us se kaha : tum darwazey hi par baitho (andar na aao ( . phir wo ( ghar mein) dakhil huey aur apni talwaar utha li to Haris ne bura anjam mehsus kar liya aur chal diya."
50,"( Abdullah (bin Aun se riwayat hai, kaha : Ibrahim ( Nakhai ( ne ham se kaha : tum log Mughira bin Saeed aur abu abdur-Raheem se bach kar raho, wo kazzaab hain"
51,"hamein Aasim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : ham bilkul nau (9) umr ladkey they jo abu Abdur-Rehman Salma ke paas hazir hotey they, wo ham se kaha kartey they : abu-Ahwas ke siwa doosrey qissa go'on (waaizon) ki majlison mein mat baitho aur Shaqiq se bach kar raho. Shaqiq khawaarij ka nuqta nazar rakhta tha, ye abu-waayel nahi (balke Shaqiq zabi hai.)"
52,"Jarir kehtey hain : main jaabir-bin-Yazeed jau'fii se mila to maine us se hadis na likhi , wo raj'at (nabi ya imam ke dobara lautkar aane ke aqeede) par eman rakhta tha."
53,"Misar ne kaha : ham se jaabir-bin-Yazeed (jau'fii) ne un bid'aton se pahley, jo us ne ghadiin, hadis bayan ki."
54,"Sufiyan ne kaha : Jaabir ne jis ( aqeedey (ka izhar kya uske izhar se pahley log us se hadis letey they, jab us ne apna aqeeda zahir kar diya to logon ne usey uski (bayaan ki hui) hadis ke barey mein laanat-malaamat ki aur kuchh ne usey chhod diya. unse puchha gaya is ne kis cheez ka izhar kya tha? kaha raj'at (kisi Nabi ya imam ke dobara lautkar aane ke aqeede) par eman kaa."
55,jarraah-bin-maleeh kehtey hain : maine jaabir-bin-Yazeed ( jau'fii ( ko ye kehtey suna : mere paas abu-Jafar ( Muhammad baaqar-bin-Ali-bin-husain-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ki 70 hazaar hadisein hain jo sab ki sab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (riwaayat ki gai) hain.
56,"Zuhair kehtey hain : Jaabir ne kaha ya maine Jaabir (bin Yazeed ( ko ye kehtey suna : bila shubah mere paas pachaas hazaar hadisein ( aisi ( hain jin mein se maine koi hadis bayan nahi ki, phir aik din us ne aik hadis bayan ki aur kaha : ye (un ( pachaas hazaar hadison mein se (eik ( hai."
57,Salaam-bin abi mutee' kehtey hain : maine Jaabir jau'fii ko ye kehtey suna : mere paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (riwaayat ki hui ( pachaas hazaar ahaadeesein hain.
58,"Sufiyan (bin Uena ( ne kaha : maine aik aadmi se suna, us ne Jaabir se irshaad-rabbaanii : فلن أبرح الأرض حتى يأذن لي أبي أو يحكم الله لي وهو خير الحاكمين""ab mein us zamin se hargiz na hiloonga yahan tak ke mera bap mujhey ijazat de ya Allah mere liye faisla kar de aur wo sab faisla karne walon se behtar hai."" ke barey mein sawal kya, to Jaabir ne kaha : uski tafseer abhi zahir nahi hui. Sufiyan ne kaha : aur us ne ye jhoot bola. to ham ne Sufiyan se kaha is se murad uski kya thi? unhon-ne kaha : rawaafiz kehtey hain : Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) badalon mein hain. unki aulad mein se jo koi khurooj (hukoomat k khilaf baghaawat) karega ham uske sath khurooj nahi karengey yahan tak ke aasman ki taraf se pukarney wala (uski murad Hazrat Ali se hai) pukaarey. yaqinan wahi pukaarega ke falan ke sath (milkar) khurooj karo. Jaabir kehta tha : ye us aayat ki tafseer hai aur usne jhoot kaha, ye aayat Hazrat Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke bhaiyon ke barey mein (naazil hui) thi."
59,"Sufiyan se riwayat hai, kaha : maine Jaabir ko taqriban tees hazaar hadisein bayan kartey huey suna hai. main unmein se aik hadis bayan karna bhi halal nahi samajhta , chahey (iske badley ( mere liye itna aur itna ho. (imaam) Muslim ne kaha : maine Abu-Ghassan Muhammad-bin Amr Razi se suna, kaha : maine Jarir bin abdul-Hameed se poochha, maine kaha : (ye jo ( Haris bin haseera hai, aap us se miley hain? kaha : haan, lambi khamoshi wala boodha hai. aik bahut badi baat par israar karta hai."
60,"Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Hammad-bin-Zaid se riwayat ki, kaha : Ayub ne aik din aik shakhs ka zikr kya aur kaha : wo zaban ka jhoota (tohmat lagaanewaalaa aur bd-zabaani karnewaala) tha aur doosrey ka zikr kya to kaha : wo raqam (cheezon par likhi hui qeemat) mein izafa kar deta tha."
61,"Sulaimaan-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne bayan kya, kaha : Ayub ne kaha : mera aik padausi hai, phir (parhezgaarii mein) uski fazeelat ka zikr kya, agar wo mere samney 2 khajhooron ke barey mein gawahi de to main (is mein bhi) uski shahadat qaabile-qabool na samjhoonga."
62,"Mamar ne kaha, maine Ayub ko kabhi kisi ki peeth peechhey usey bura kehtey nahi suna, siwaey abdul-kareem, yani abu-Umayya ke. unhon-ne iska zikr kya to kaha, Allah is par raham karey, ghair qaabile-bharosa hai, usne mujhse Ikrima se riwayat ki gaee aik hadis ke barey mein sawal kya, phir (logon se) kaha : maine Ikrima se suna hai."
63,"Affaan-bin-Muslim ne kaha : Hammam ne ham se bayan kya, kaha : Abu-Dawud aama hamarey yahan aaya aur ye kehna shuru kar diya : hamein Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai aur hamein Zaid-bin-Arqam (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki. ham ne ye baat Qatada ko batai , unhon-ne kaha is ne jhoot bola. us ne unse nahi suna, wo to aik mangtaa tha, aur taaoon (ek tarah ki bimari ke dauraan) mein logon ke samney hath phailaataa phirtaa tha."
64,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Hammam ne khabar di ke Abu-Dawud aama Qatada ke yahan aaya, jab wo khada hua (aur chala gaya) to logon ne kaha : usey ye zaum hai ke usne atthaara Badri sahaba se mulaqat ki. is par Qatada kehney lagey : (taaoon ki) wabaaey-aam se pahley ye aik mangtaa tha, iska (ilme-hadees) aisi kisi cheez se koi sarokaar na tha, wo us barey mein baat tak na karta tha. ba-khuda na Hasan (Basrii) ne (kabhii) kisi Badri se bilaa-waasta hadis hamein sunai, na Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne aik sa'd-bin-maalik (Raziallahu anhu) ke siwa kisi aur Badri se baraahe-raast suni hui koi hadis sunai."
65,"Jarir ne raqba (bin masqala bin-Abdullah abdii koofii (Rahmatullahi-alaih) Jaleelul-qadr taaba'ii) se riwayat ki ke abu-Jafar ( abdullaah-bin-mas'ood-bin-a'un-bin-ja'far-bin-abii taalib) haashmii madaainii hadison ghadaa karta tha, sachchai (ya hikmat) par mabni kalam (pesh kartaa) wo kalam Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke faraameen mein se na hota tha lekin usey wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat karta tha."
66,"Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi ne Shoba se, unhon-ne yoonus-bin-ubaid se riwayat kartey huey bayan kya, (yoonus ne) kaha : Amr-bin-Ubaid (ma'roof moa'tazilii jo pahley Hazrat hasan-Basrii ki majlis mein hazir raha karta tha) hadis (ki riwaayat) mein jhoot bola karta tha."
67,Muaaz-bin-Muaaz kehtey hain : maine Auf-bin-abii jameela se kaha : Amr-bin-Ubaid ne Hazrat Hasan Basri se (riwaayat kartey huey) ye hadis sunai : jisne ham par hathiyar uthaya to wo ham mein se nahi. unhon-ne kaha : b-khudaa ! Amr ne (is hadis ki riwayat Hasan Basri ki taraf mansub karne mein) jhoot bola lekin wo chahta hai ke us ( sahi hadis) ko apni jhooti baat se mila de.
68,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar qawaareerii ne kaha : ham se Hammad-bin-Zaid ne bayan kya, kaha : aik aadmi tha, wo Ayub sakhtiyan ki ilmi majlis mein betha karta tha aur unse hadisein suna karta tha. Ayub ne usey ghair hazir pa kar uske barey mein puchha to logon ne bataya : janab Abu-Bakar (Ayyoob ki kunniyat)! wo Amr-bin-Ubaid se munsalik ho gaya hai. Hammad ne kaha : aik din mein Ayub ke sath tha, ham subah sawerey bazar ki taraf gaey to us aadmi ne Ayub ka istiqbaal kya. Ayub ne usey salam kaha aur (haal ahwaal) poochha, phir Ayub kehney lagey : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke tum us aadmi ke sath jud gaey ho. Hammad ne kaha : unhon-ne iska, yani Amr ka naam liya. wo kehney laga : haan, janab Abu-Bakr! wo ajeeb w ghareeb baatein (jinhein koi nahi jaantaa) hamarey samney laataa hai. kaha : Ayub us se kehney lagey : ham unhi ajeebo-ghareeb baton se bhaagtey hain ya dartey hain (ke ye jhooti aur man-ghadat hoti hain.)"
69,"Sulaimaan-bin-Harab ne kaha : ham se ibne-zaid , yani Hammad ne bayan kya, kaha : Ayub se puchha gaya : Amr-bin-Ubaid ne Hazrat Hasan Basri se riwayat bayan ki hai (ke unhon-ne ( kaha : jisey nabeez ( sharab ( se nasha ho jaey usey kode na maarey jaaein. to unhon-ne ( Ayub sakhtiyan ( ne kaha is ne jhoot bola, maine ( khud) Hasan se suna, wo kehtey they : jisey nabeez se nasha ho jaey usey kode maarey jaaein."
70,"Salaam-bin abi mutee' kehtey hain. janab Ayub sakhtiyan ko ye khabar pahunchi ke main Amr (bin Ubaid (ke yahan ( dars mein) jata hun to aik din wo mere paas aaey aur kaha, tum ne ghaur kya aik aisa aadmi aaya jiske Deen par tumhen eitibaar na ho, tum uski hadis par kaisey aitimad karogey !"
71,"Sufiyan ne bayan kya, kaha : maine abu-Musa ( Israel bin-Musa Basri , nazeel hind) se suna, keh rahe they : hamein Amr-bin-Ubaid ne bidat ka shikar honey se pahley hadis sunai."
72,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : maine waasit ke qazi abu-Sheba ke barey mein malum karne ke liye Shoba ki taraf likha to unhon-ne jawab mein meri taraf likh bheja , us se koi cheez riwayat na karo aur mera khat phaad do."
73,Affaan (bin-Muslim ( ne kaha : maine Hammaad-bin-Salma ko Saaleh-murrii ke waastey se aik hadis sunai jo usney Sabit se riwayat ki to unhon-ne ( Hammad ( kaha is ne jhoot bola. (usi tarah) maine Hammam ko Saaleh-murrii se aik hadis sunai to unhon-ne bhi kaha is ne jhoot bola.
74,"Abu-Dawud ne bayan kya, kaha : Shoba ne mujh se kaha : Jareer-bin-Haazim ke paas jao aur us se kaho : tumharey liye halal nahi ke tum Hasan-bin-Umaara se ( hadis) riwayat karo kyonke wo jhoot boltaa hai. Abu-Dawud ne kaha : maine Shoba se kaha : wo kaisey ? to unhon-ne kaha is ne hamein Hakam se (riwaayat ki hui ( hadison sunain jinki ham ne asl na paai . (kaha ( maine kaha : kya cheez riwayat ki? kaha : maine Hakam se kaha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud ke shaheedon ki namaaze-janaaza ada farmaaii? to unhon-ne jawab diya : aap ne unki namaaze-janaaza nahi padhi ( jabke ( Hasan-bin-Umaara ne Hakam hi se Miqsam ke hawale se Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se ye riwayat bayan ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki namaaze-janaaza padhi aur unhein dafn kya. (usi tarah) maine Hakam se puchha : aap zina se paida hui aulad ke barey mein kya kehtey hain? kaha : unka janaaza padha jaeyga maine puchha : ye riwayat kis hawale se bayan ki jati hai, kaha : Hazrat Hasan Basri se ( jabke ( Hasan-bin-Umaara ne kaha : ham se Hakam ne Yahyaa-bin-Jazaar ke hawale se ye riwayat Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan ki."
75,"Hasan Hulwani ne kaha : maine Yazid-bin-Harun se suna, unhon-ne Ziyaad-bin-Memoon ka zikr kartey huey kaha : maine Halaf uthaya hai ke main us se aur Khalid-bin mahdooj se kabhi riwayat na karunga (aur kaha : ( mein Ziyaad-bin-Memoon se mila, us se aik hadis sunaney ka kaha to usne mujhey wo hadis Bakr Muzni se riwayat karke sunai, phir ( kuchh waqt baad) mein dobara uske paas gaya to usne wahi hadis muwarriq se bayan ki, phir aik baar aur uske paas gaya to usne wahi hadis Hasan ( Basri) se sunai. wo ( Yazid-bin-Harun ( un donon ( Ziyaad-bin-Memoon aur Khalid-bin mahdooj ( ko jhoot ki taraf mansub kartey they. Hulwani ne kaha : maine Abdus-Samad se hadis suni aur unke samney Ziyaad-bin-Memoon ka zikr kya to unhon-ne uski nisbat jhoot ki taraf ki."
76,"Mehmood-bin Ghelaan ne kaha : maine Abu-Dawud Tiyalisi se kaha : aap ne Ibaad-bin-Mansoor se bahut zyada riwaayatein li hain, phir kya hua ke aap ne utara wali riwayat jo Nazar-bin-Shumail ne hamarey samney bayan ki, unse nahi sunii? unhon-ne mujh se kaha : khamosh raho, main aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi Ziyaad-bin-Memoon se miley aur us se poochhtey huey kaha : ye hadison jo tum Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kartey ho (kya hain?) to wo kehney laga : tum donon dekho ke aik aadmi gunah karta hai, phir tauba kar leta hai to kya Allah uski tauba qabool nahi karta ! kaha : ham ne kaha : haan. usne kaha : maine un ( hadison ( mein se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kuchh nahi suna, na kam na zyada , agar log nahi jantey to (kya) tum donon bhi nahi jantey ke main Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se nahi milaa!  Abu-Dawud ne kaha : phir hamein ye khabar pahunchi ke wo ( wahi ( riwaayatein bayan karta hai to main aur Abdur-Rehman uske paas aaey to wo kehney laga : main tauba karta hun, phir iske baad bhi wo wahi hadisein bayan karta tha to ham ne usey (iske haal par) chhod diya."
77,"Hasan Hulwani ne bayan kya, kaha : maine Shababaa se suna (kaha : Abdul-Quddoos hamarey samney hadis bayan karta tha aur kehta tha : Suwed-bin-Aqla) Shababaa ne kaha : maine Abdul-Quddoos se suna, kehta tha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne, 'Rauh ko zameen,' banaaney se mana farmaya hai (kahaa) us se kaha gaya : iska kya matlab hai? to usne kaha : matlab ye hai ke diwar mein suraakh rakha jaey taake usmein hawa dakhil ho. (imaam) Muslim ne kaha : maine Ubaidullah-bin-Umar qawaareerii se suna, keh rahe they : maine Hammad-bin-Zaid se suna, wo (Mahdii-bin-Hilaal ke ilmi majlis lagaane ke kuchh din baad) aik aadmi se keh rahe they : ye namkeen chashma kya hai jo aap ki taraf se phootaa hai? usne kaha : haan , aey abu-Ismaaiil! (aap ki baat theek hai)."
78,"Affaan ne kaha : maine abu-Awana se suna, kaha : mujhey Hasan ( Basri) se koi hadis na pahunchi magar main usey Abaan-bin-abii-Ayaash ke paas ley gaya to usne usey mere samney padha ."
79,"Ali-bin-Mus-hir ne bayan kya, kaha : maine aur Hamza Zayyat ne Abaan-bin-abii-Ayaash se taqriban aik hazaar hadison sunein . Ali ne kaha : phir ( kuchh waqt baad) mein Hamza se mila to usne mujhey bataya ke usne khuwab main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha to wo hadison jo Aban se suni thin aap ki khidmat mein pesh kin. aap ne unmein bahut maamooli hissey , panch ya chh hadison ke siwa kisi cheez ko na pehchaana ."
80,"Zakariiyaa-bin Adi ne kaha : mujh se Abu-Ishaq fazari ne kaha : Baqiiya se wahi hadison likho jo usney Maruf logon se riwayat ki hain, wo na likho jo usney ghair Maruf logon se riwayat ki hain aur Ismail bin Ayash se, jo usney Maruf logon se riwayat kiin ya ghair Maruf se, kuchh na likho ."
81,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim Hanzali ne bayan kya, kaha : maine Abdullah ke ashaab ( shaagirdon) mein se aik se suna, kaha : ibne-Mubarak ne farmaya : Baqiiya achchha aadmi hai agar ye naamon ko kunniyaton se badal deta aur kunniyaton ko naamon se. wo aik zamaney tak hamein abu-Saeed w haazii se riwaayatein sunata raha, ham ne achi tarah ghaur kya to wo Abdul-Quddoos nikla ."
82,"Abdur-Razzaq kehtey hain : maine ibne-Mubarak ko) aisa kartey ( nahi dekha ke wo khul kar apni ye baat ( raey ( keh dein ke falan jhoota hai, siwaey Abdul-Quddoos ke. maine unhein khud ye kehtey suna ke wo jhoota hai."
83,"Abdullah-bin Abdur-Rehman Darmi ne mujh se bayan kya, kaha : maine abu-Naeem se suna (aur unhon-ne Mu-allaa-bin-Irfaan ka zikr kya (aur kaha : usne kaha : ham se abu-Waail ne bayan kya, kaha : safain mein ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) hamarey samney nikley to abu-Naeem ne kaha : unke barey mein tumhari raey hai ke wo maut ke baad dobara zinda ho gaey they?"
84,"Affaan-bin-Muslim se riwayat hai, kaha : ham Ismaaeel-bin-Ulaih ke yahan they, to aik aadmi ne aik doosrey aadmi se riwayat ( bayan ( ki. maine kaha : wo mazbut (qaabile-bharosa ke jaisa) nahi. to us aadmi ne kaha : tum ne uski gheebat ki hai. Ismail kehney lagey : unhon-ne uski gheebat nahi ki balke Hukm (faisla) bayan kya hai wo (sabt) nahi hai."
85,"Bishr-bin-Umar ne ham se bayan kya, kaha : maine imam Malik-bin-Anas se Muhammad-bin Abdur-Rehman ke barey mein puchha jo Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se hadison riwayat karta hai to unhon-ne kaha : wo qaabile-bharosa nahi. maine Malik-bin-Anas se abu-Huwairis ke barey mein sawal kya to unhon-ne farmaya : wo qaabile-bharosa nahi. ( phir ( maine unse us Shoba ke barey mein sawal kya jis se ibne-abi-Ze-ib riwayat kartey hain to farmaya : wo qaabile-bharosa nahi. maine unse Saleh Maula Tawaama ke barey mein sawal kya to kaha : qaabile-bharosa nahi. maine unse haram bin Usman ke barey mein puchha to farmaya : qaabile-bharosa nahi. maine Imam Malik se un panchon ke barey mein poochha, unhon-ne farmaya : ye sab hadis ke bayan karne mein qaabile-bharosa nahi. maine unse aik aur shakhs ke barey mein puchha jiska ( ab ( mein naam bhool gaya hon to unhon-ne kaha : kya tum ne meri kitaabon mein iska naam dekha hai. maine kaha : nahi. farmaya : agar qaabile-bharosa hota to tum iska zikr meri kitaabon mein dekhtey ."
86,"ham se Hajjaj ne bayan kya, kaha : ham se ibne-abi-Ze-ib ne Shurehbil bin Sad ke hawale se hadis bayan ki aur wo muttahim (Jis par jhoot ka ilzam laga ho) thaa."
87,"Abu-Ishaq Taliqani kehtey hain : maine Abdullah-bin-Mubarak se suna, keh rahe they : (eik waqt tha) agar mujhey ikhtiyar diya jata ke jannat mein dakhil hon ya Abdullah-bin muharrir se miloon to main iska intikhab karta ke pahley mein us se mil loon phir jannat mein jaunga, phir jab maine usey dekh liya to iske muqaabley mein aik mengni bhi mujhey zyada behtar lagi"
88,"Waleed-bin-Saaleh ne bayan kya, kaha : Ubaidullaah-bin-Amr ne kaha : Zaid , yani ibne-abi Aneesa ne kaha : mere bhai ( Yahya-bin-abi-Unaisa ( se riwayat na lo."
89,"Abdullah-bin Jafar Raqii ne Ubaidullaah-bin-Amr ke hawale se bayan kya, kaha : Yahya-bin-abi-Unaisa jhoota tha."
90,"Hammad-bin-Zaid se riwayat hai, kaha : Ayub sakhtiyan ke samney Farqad ka zikr kya gaya to unhon-ne kaha : Farqad hadis (ki maharat rakhney) wala nahi."
91,"mujh se Abdur-Rehman bin Bishr abdii ne bayan kya, kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan se suna, jab unke samney Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Ubaid-bin-Umair Lesi ka zikr kya gaya to unhon-ne usey intihai zaeef qarar diya. (imaam) Yahya se kaha gaya : haan. phir kaha : main nahi samajhta ke koi aik insan bhi Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Ubaid-bin-Umair se riwayat kar sakta hai."
92,"Bishr-bin-hakam ne bayan kya, kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan se suna, unhon-ne Hakeem-bin-Jubair aur Abdul-Aala ko zaeef qarar diya aur (usi tarah) Yahya ne Moosaa-bin-Diinaar ko bhi zaeef qarar diya (aur ( kaha : uski ( bayan ki hui ( hadis hawa (jaisii) hai aur Moosaa-bin-dahqaan aur Esa abi Esa madni ko) bhi) zaeef qarar diya. kaha : aur maine Hasan-bin- Esa se suna, keh rahe they : mujh se ibne-Mubarak ne farmaya : tum jab Jarir ke paas pahuncho to teen ( rawiyon ( ki hadison ke siwa iska Sara ilm likh lenaa. Ubaida-bin mau'tab , Sirii-bin Ismail aur Muhammad-bin-Saalim ki hadisein us se na likhnaa. ‏‏‏‏ Imaam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha : aur uske jaisi jo ham ne zikr kya ahale-hadees ka kalam muttahim rawiyon main aur unke uyoob bahut hain jiske bayan karne se kitab lambi ho jaeygi aur jis qadr ham ne bayan kya wo kafi hai us shakhs ke liye jo qaum ka mazhab samajh bojh jaey. ‏‏‏‏ aur hadison ke imaamon ne rawiyon ka aib khol dena zaroori samjha aur is baat ka fatwa diya. jab unse puchha gaya isliye ke ye bada aham kaam hai. kyonke Deen ki baat jab naql ki jaeygi to wo kisi baat ke halal honey ke liye hogi ya haram honey ke liye ya usmein kisi baat ka hukm hoga ya kisi baat ki manaahii hogi ya kisi kaam ki taraf raghbat dilai jaey ya kisi kaam se daraayaa jaaeyga.bahar-haal jab rawi sachcha aur amaanatdaar na ho phir us se koi riwayat karey jo iske haal ko janta ho aur wo haal doosrey se bayan na karey jo na janta ho to gunahgaar hoga aur dhokaa dene wala hoga aam musalmanon ko. isliye ke kuchh log un hadison ko sunengey aur un sab par ya kuchh par amal karengey aur shayad wo sab ya unmein se aksar jhooti hun. (aur kuchh nuskhon mein ye hai ke unmein kam ya bahut jhooti hon) jinki asl na ho halanke sahi hadisein qaabile-bharosa logon ki aur jinki riwayat par qanaa'at ho sakti hai kya kam hain ke be-eitibaar aur jinki riwayat par qanaa'at nahi ho sakti unki riwayaton ki zarurat padey. Mina aur main samajhta hun ke jin logon ne us qism ki zaeef hadisein aur majhool sanadein naql ki hain aur unmein masroof hain aur wo jantey hain unki kamzori ko, to unki gharaz ye hai ke Awam ke nazdeek apna kasarate-ilm Sabit karein aur isliye ke log kahin sub'haan Allaah! falan shakhs ne kitni zyada hadisein jama ki hain. aur jis shakhs ki ye chaal hai aur iska ye tariqa hai, uska ilm, hadis mein kuchh nahi aur wo jaahi kahlaaney ka zyada haqdaar hai aalim kahlaaney se. ‏‏‏‏ Imaam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain ke hamarey zamane mein kuchh aisey logon ne jinhoney jhoot-moot apne aapko muhaddis qarar diya hai, beech ki sihat mein aik qaul bayan kya hai. agar ham bilkul usko naql na karein aur uska radd na likhein to umda tajwiz hogi aur theek rasta hoga isliye ke ghalat baat ki taraf tawajjoh na karna usko mitaaney ke liye aur uske kehney waley ka naam khodney ke liye behtar hai aur munasib hai jaahilon ke liye taake unko khabar bhi na ho us ghalat baat ki magar us wjah se ke ham anjam ki burai se dartey hain aur ye baat dekhtey hain ke jaahi nai baat par farefta ho jatey hain aur ghalat baat par jald yaqin kar letey hain jo ulma ke nazdeek naaqaabile-bharosa hoti hai, hamne us qaul ki ghalati bayan karna aur usko radd karna iska bura hona aur jhoot hona aur kharabiyan zikr karna logon ke liye behtar aur faayde-mand khayal kya aur iska anjam bhi nek hoga agar izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah chaahey. Mina aur us shakhs ne jiske qaul se ham ne guftgu shuru ki aur jiske fikr aur khayal ko ham ne baatil kaha yun guman kya hai ke jo asnaad aisi hon jis mein 'fulaan se fulaan' ho aur ye baat malum ho gaee ke wo donon aik zamane mein they aur mumkin ho ke ye hadis aik ne doosrey se suni ho aur usse mila ho magar ham ko ye malum nahi hua ke usne us se suna hai, na hamne kisi riwayat mein is baat ki tasreeh paai ke wo donon miley they aur unmein munh dar munh baat cheet hui thi to aisi sanadon se jo hadis riwayat ki jaey wo hujjat nahi hai jab tak ye baat malum na ho ke kam se kam wo donon apni umr mein aik baar miley they aur aik ne doosrey se baat cheet ki thi ya aisi koi hadis riwayat ki jaey jis mein us baat kaa bayan ho ke un donon ki mulaqat aik ya zyada baar hui thi. agar is baat ka ilm na ho aur na koi hadis aisi riwayat ki jaey jis se mulaqat aur samaa, ka saboot ho to aisi hadis naql karna jis se mulaqat ka ilm na ho aisi haalat mein hujjat nahi hai aur wo hadis moquf rahegii, yahan tak ke un donon ka samaa, thoda ya bahut dusri riwayat se malum ho. aur ye qaul asnaad ke baab mein Allah tujh par raham karey aik nayaa eiijaad kya hua hai jo pahley kisi ne nahi kaha na hadis ke aalimon ne uski muwafiqat ki hai isliye ke mashhoor mazhab jis par ittifaq hai ahale-ilm ka agley aur pichhlon ka, wo ye hai ke jab koi qaabile-bharosa shakhs kisi qaabile-bharosa shakhs se riwayat karey aik hadis ko aur un donon ki mulaqat jaaiz aur mumkin ho (umr aur saal k lihaaz se) us wjah se ke wo donon aik zamaney mein maujood they, agarche kisi hadis mein is baat ki wazaahat na ho ke wo donon miley they ya unmein roo-baroo baat cheet hui thi to wo hadis hujjat hai aur wo riwayat Sabit hai. albatta agar us baat ki wahan koi khuli daleel ho ke dar-haqiqat ye rawi doosrey rawi se nahi mila ya us se kuchh nahi suna to wo hadis hujjat na hogi lekin jab tak ye baat mubham rahe (yani golmol aur koi daleel na sunney aur na milney ki na ho) to sirf mulaqat ka mumkin hona kafi hoga aur is riwayat ke baare me taslim kiya jaayega ki ismein samaa, Sabit hai. ‏‏phir jis shakhs ne ye qaul nikala hai ya uski himaayat karta hai us se yun guftgu karengey ke khud terey hi sarey kalam se ye baat nikli ke aik qaabile-bharosa shakhs ki riwayat doosrey qaabile-bharosa shakhs se hujjat hai jis par amal karna wajib hai. phir tone khud aik shart baad mein badha di ke jab ye baat malum ho jaey ke wo donon apni umr mein aik baar miley they ya zyada aur aik ne doosrey se suna tha. ab us shart ka saboot kisi aisey shakhs ke qaul se paanaa hai jiska maannaa zaroori ho. agar aisa qaul nahi hai to aur koi daleel apne da'wey par laanaa. ‏‏‏‏ agar wo ye kahey ke is baab mein salaf ka qaul hai yani us shart ke saboot ke liye to kaha jaeyga kahan hai? la ! phir na usko koi qaul milega aur na kisi aur ko aur agar wo aur koi daleel qaaim karna chahey to poochhegey wo daleel kya hai? Mina phir agar wo shakhs ye kahey : maine ye mazhab isliye ikhtiyar kya hai ke maine hadis ke tamam agley aur pichhley rawiyon ko dekha ke aik doosrey se hadis riwayat kartey hain halanke us aik ne doosrey ko dekha hai na usse suna to jab maine dekha ke unhon-ne jaaiz rakha hai mursal ko riwayat karna baghair samaa, ke aur mursal riwayat hamarey aur ilm walon ke nazdeek hujjat nahi hai to zarurat padi mujh ko rawi ke samaa, dekhney ki jis ko wo riwayat karta hai doosrey se. phir agar mujhey kahin zara bhi Sabit ho gaya ke usne suna hai doosrey rawi se to uski tamam riwaayatein usse durust ho gaiin. agar bilkul mujhey malum na hua ke usne usse suna hai to main riwayat ko moquf rakhoonga aur mere nazdeek wo riwayat hujjat na hogi isliye ke mumkin hai iska mursal hona (daleel ho mukhalif ki. ab iska jawab aagey mazkoor hota hai). Mina to usse kaha jaeyga agar terey nazdeek hadis ko zaeef karne ki aur usko hujjat na samajhney ki illat sirf irsaal ka mumkin hona hai (jaisey usne khud kaha ke jab samaa, Sabit na ho to wo riwayat hujjat na hogi kyonke mumkin hai iska mursal honaa) to lazim aata hai ke to kisi asnaad ko na maaney jab tak awwal se lekar aakhir tak usmein tasreeh na ho samaa, ki (yani har rawi doosrey se yun riwayat karey ke maine us se sunaa) maslan jo hadis ham ko pahunchi Hisham ki riwayat se, usne apne bap Urwa se, usne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna hai jaisey ham is baat ko bil-yaqeen jantey hain ke Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai bawajud iske is baat ki gunjaaish zaroor hai ke agar kisi riwayat mein Hisham yun na kahey ke maine Urwa se suna hai ya Urwa ne mujhey khabar di (balke sirf (Urwa se) kahey) to Hisham aur Urwa ke beech mein aik aur shakhs ho jisne Urwa se sun kar Hisham ko khabar di ho aur khud Hisham ne apne bap se is riwayat ko na suna ho lekin Hisham ne usko mursalan riwayat karna chaha aur jiske zariey se suna iska zikr munasib na jana aur jaisey ye ehtimaal Hisham aur Urwa ke beech mein hai, waisey hi Urwa aur Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke beech mein ho sakta hai. isi tarah har aik asnaad mein jis mein samaa, ki tasreeh nahi bhale hi ye baat malum ho jaey ke aik ne doosrey se bahut si riwaayatein suni hain. magar ye ho sakta hai ke kuchh riwaayatein us se na suni hon balke kisi aur ke zariey se sun kar usko mursalan naql kya ho par jiske zariey se suna iska naam na liya aur kabhi us ijmaa 'ko rafa' karne ke liye iska naam bhi ley diya aur irsaal ko tark kya. ‏‏‏‏ Imaam Muslim (Rahmatullahi-alaih) farmatey hain ke ye ehtimaal jo ham ne bayan kya (sarf farzii aur khayaalii nahi hai) balke maujood hai hadis main aur jari hai bahut se qaabile-bharosa muhaddeseen ki riwayaton mein. ham thodi si aisi riwaayatein bayan kartey hain Allah chahey to unse daleel poori hogi bahut si riwayaton par. pehli riwayat wo hai jo Ayub sakhtiyan aur ibne-Mubarak aur Wakee aur ibne-numair aur aik jamat ne siwaey unke Hisham se naql ki, usne apne bap Urwa se, usne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ke main khushbu lagaatii Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ehram kholtey waqt aur ehram baandhtey waqt jo sabse umda mujh ko miltii. usi riwayat ko jyon ka tyon Lais-bin-Sad aur Dawud attaar aur Humaid bin Aswad aur Wuhaib bin Khalid aur abu-Usama ne Hisham se riwayat kya. Hisham ne kaha : khabar di mujh ko Usman bin Urwa ne, usne Urwa se, usne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. ‏‏‏‏ doosrii riwayat Hisham ki hai, apne bap Urwa se, usne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab aetikaf mein hotey to apna sar meri taraf jhukaa detey. mein aap ke sar mein kanghi kar deti halanke main haaiza hoti. usi riwayat ko jyon ka tyon Imam Malik (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne Zohri se riwayat kya hai. usne Urwa se, usne Umra se, usne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. teesrii riwayat wo hai jo Zohri aur Saleh bin abi Hassan ne abu-Salma se naql kya usne Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bosa letey they aur aap roze-daar hotey . Yahya-bin-abi-Kasir ne us bose ki hadis ko yun riwayat kya khabar di mujhey abu-Salma-bin-Abdur-Rehman ne, unko khabar di Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ne unko khabar di Urwa ne unko Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unka bosa letey aur aap roze-daar hotey. ‏‏‏‏ chauthii riwayat wo hai jo Sufiyan-bin-Uena wghaira ne Amr-bin-Dinar se ki, unhon-ne Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham ko khilaaya ghodon ka gosht aur mana kya paaltu gadhon ke gosht se. isi hadis ko riwayat kya Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Amr se, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin Ali (yani imam Baaqar ( se, unhon-ne Jaabir se (to Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Amr-bin-Dinar aur Jaabir ke beech mein aik waasta aur naql kya Muhammad-bin Ali ka jo pehli asnaad mein nahin) aur usi qism ki hadisein bahut hain jinka shumaar bahut hai aur jitni ham ne bayan kiin wo samajhney walon ke liye kafi hain. Mina phir jab illat us shakhs ke nazdeek jiska qaul ham ne uper bayan kya hadis ki kharabi aur tauheen ye hui ke aik rawi ka samaa, jab doosrey rawi se malum na ho to irsaal mumkin hai to iske qaul ke b-mojib usko lazim aata hai tark karna hujjat ka un riwayaton ke sath jinke rawi ka samaa, doosrey se malum ho chuka hai (lekin khas is riwayat mein samaa, ki tasreeh nahin) albatta us shakhs ke nazdeek sirf wahi riwayat hujjat hogi jis mein samaa, ki tasreeh hai kyonkey uper ham bayan kar chukey hain ke hadis riwayat karne waley imaamon ka haal mukhtalif hota hai kabhi to wo irsaal kartey aur jis se unhon-ne suna ho iska naam nahi letey aur kabhi khush hotey aur hadis ki poori asnaad jis tarah se unhon-ne suna hai, bayan kar detey phir agar unko utaar hota to utaar batlatey aur jo chadhaao hota to chadhaao batlatey jaisey ham uper saaf bayan kar chukey hain. Mina aur ham ne salaf ke imaamon mein se jo hadis ko istemal kartey they aur asnaad ki sihat ko malum kartey they jaisey Ayub sakhtiyan aur ibne-Aun aur Malik-bin-Anas aur Sho'ba-bin-Hujjaaj aur Yahya-bin-Saeed qattaan aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi aur jo unke baad hain kisi ko nahi suna ke wo asnaad mein samaa, ki tahqeeq kartey hon jaisey ye shakhs dawa karta hai jiska qaul uper ham ne bayan kya. albatta jinhoney unmein se rawiyon ke samaa, ki tahqeeq ki hai to wo un rawiyon ke jo mashhoor hain tadlees mein. is waqt beshak aisey rawiyon ke samaa, se behas kartey hain aur uski malum kartey hain taake unse tadlees ka marz door ho jaey lekin samaa, ki tahqeeq us rawi mein jo mudallis (hadees ka wo raawi jo hadis ka silsile na bataaye) na ho jis tarah us shakhs ne bayan kya to ye ham ne kisi imam se nahi suna un imaamon mein se jinka zikr ham ne kya aur jinka nahi kya. ‏‏‏‏ is qism ki riwayat mein se Abdullah-bin Yazeed Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki riwayat hai (jo khud sahabi hain) unhon-ne dekha hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aur riwayat ki hai Huzefa bin Yamaan aur Abu-Masood ( Aqba-bin-Amr Ansari badrii) se, har aik se eik-eik hadis ko jis ko unhon-ne jama kya hai Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tak, magar un riwayaton mein is baat ki tasreeh nahi ke Abdullah-bin Yazeed ne suna un donon se (yani Huzefa aur Abu-Masood se sunaa) aur na kisi riwayat mein ham ne ye baat paai ke Abdullah, Huzefa aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se roo-baroo miley aur unse koi hadis suni aur na kahin ham ne paya ke Abdullah ne un donon ko dekha kisi khalis riwayat mein (magar chunkey Abdullah khud sahabi they) aur uski umr itni thi ke mulaqat unki Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) aur Abu-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se mumkin hai isliye riwayat 'An' ke sath mahmool hai ittisaal par to sirf imkan mulaqat kafi hua jaisey Imam Muslim ka mazhab hai aur kisi ilm waley se nahi suna gaya na agley logon se, na unse jin se ham miley hain ke unhon-ne ta'an kya ho un donon hadison mein jinko Abdullah ne riwayat kya Huzefa aur abi Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se ke ye zaeef hain balke ye hadisein aur jo unke jaise hain sahi hadison mein se hain aur qawii hain un imaamon ke nazdeek jin se ham miley hain aur wo unka istemal jaaiz rakhtey hain aur unse hujjat letey hain halanke yahi hadisein us shakhs ke nazdeek jiska qaul uper ham ne bayan kya (jo saboot mulaqat shart karta hai) waahii hain aur be-kaar hain jab tak samaa, Abdullah ka Huzefa aur abu Masood se tahqeeq na ho chuki ho. Mina aur agar ham sab aisi hadison ko, jo ahale-ilm ke nazdeek sahi hain aur us shakhs ke nazdeek zaeef hain, bayan karein to unka zikr kartey kartey ham thak jaaengey (is qadr kasarat se hain) lekin ham chahtey hain ke thodi unmein se bayan karein taake baqi ke liye wo namoona hun. ‏‏‏‏ abu Usman nehdi (Abdur-Rehmaan bin mil jo aik so tees baras ke ho kar marey) aur abu-Raafe Saaigh (naqeea madni ( un donon ne zamana jahiliyat ka paya hai (lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat muyassar na hui aisey logon ko mukhzim kehtey hain) aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke badey-badey Badri sahaabiyon se miley hain aur riwaayatein ki hain. phir unse hat kar aur sahaba se yahan tak ke Abu-Hurera aur ibne-Umar aur unke manind (tarah) sahaabiyon se, unmein se har aik ne aik hadis Ubai-bin-Kab se riwayat ki hai, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se halanke kisi riwayat se ye Sabit nahi hui ke un donon ne Ubai-bin-Kab ko dekha ya unse kuchh sunaa. aur abu-Amr Shebani ( Sad bin Ayas ( ne jisne jahiliyat ka zamana paya hai aur wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein jawan mard tha aur abu-Ma'mar Abdullaah-bin-Sanjara ne har aik ne unmein se 2-2 hadisein Abu-Masood Ansari se riwayat kin, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Ubaid-bin-Umair ne, Ummul-Momenin Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se aik hadis riwayat ki unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, aur Ubaid paida huey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane main aur Qais-bin abi Hazim ne jisne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zamana paya hai Abu-Masood Ansari se teen hadisein riwayat kiin aur Abdur-Rehman bin abi Laila ne jisne saiyedna umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai aur saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat mein rahaa. eik hadis Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki aur Rabaii-binHaraash ne Imran-bin-Husain se 2 hadisein riwayat kin, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Abu-Bakra se aik hadis , unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Rabaii ne saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna hai aur unse riwayat ki hai aur Naafe bin Juber bin Mut-im ne abu-Shuraih Khuzai se aik hadis riwayat ki. unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Nauman bin abi Ayash ne Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se teen hadisein riwayat kiin unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Ata-bin-Yazeed Lesi ne Tameem daari se aik hadis riwayat ki unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Sulaiman-bin-Yasar ne Rafe-bin-Khadeej se aik hadis riwayat ki unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aur Ubaid bin Abdur-Rehman Himyari ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se kai hadisein riwayat kiin unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. Mina phir ye sab Tabe-een (Rahmatullahi-alaih) jinhoney sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki hai jinka zikr ham ne uper kya, unka samaa, un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se kisi muaiyan riwayat mein malum nahi hua, na mulaqat hi un sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath riwayat se zahir hui bawajud iske ye sab riwaayatein hadis aur riwayat ke pahchaanney walon ke nazdeek (yani aimma hadis ke nazdeek ( sahi sanad hain aur ham nahi jantey ke kisi ne unmein se kisi riwayat ko zaeef kaha ho ya usmein samaa, ki talash ki ho, isliye ke samaa, mumkin hai iska inkar nahi ho sakta kyonke wo donon aik zamane mein maujood they aur ye qaul jis ko us shakhs ne nikala hai jiska bayan uper ham ne kya hadis ke zaeef honey ke liye us illat ki wjah se mazkoor hui us laaiq bhi nahi ke us taraf tawajjoh karein ya iska zikr karein, isliye ke ye qaul nayaa nikala hua hai aur ghalat aur faasid hai koi ahale-ilm salaf mein se iska qaail nahi hua aur jo log salaf ke baad guzrey unhon-ne iska inkar kya to us se iske radd karne ki haajat nahi. jab us qaul ki aur uske kehney waley ki ye waq'at hai jaisey bayan hui aur Allah madad karne wala hai is baat ko radd karne ke liye jo aalimon ke mazhab ke khilaf hai aur usi par bharosa hai. tamam hua muqaddima Muslim kaa. ab shuru hota hai bayan eman ka jo asl hai tamam aamaal ka aur jis par moquf hai nijat aakhirat ke azab se."
